flowchart TD
    user[Пользователь CMDBuild] --> ui[CMDBuild Web UI]
    ui --> cmdb[CMDBuild]
    cmdb -->|POST /webhooks/cmdbuild| wh[cmdbwebhooks2kafka]
    wh -->|cmdbuild.webhooks.*| kafka[(Kafka)]
    kafka --> conv[cmdbkafka2zabbix]
    conv -->|zabbix.host.requests.*| kafka
    kafka --> api[zabbixrequests2api]
    api -->|JSON-RPC| zabbix[Zabbix API]
    api -->|zabbix.host.responses.*| kafka
    wh -->|logs| logs[Kafka log topics]
    conv -->|logs| logs
    api -->|logs| logs
    logs -. future .-> elk[ELK]

    subgraph fallback[Fallback для update/delete без zabbix_hostid]
        api -->|host.get| zabbix
        api -->|host.update или host.delete| zabbix
    end
